article.description: — Jyare Davis scored 16 points as Delaware beat Brown 67-59 on Friday.
article.headline: Delaware wins 67-59 against Brown
article.story: NASSAU, Bahamas -- — Jyare Davis scored 16 points as Delaware beat Brown 67-59 on Friday. Davis also had seven rebounds for the Fightin' Blue Hens (5-0). Jalun Trent scored 14 points while going 6 of 11 and 2 of 4 from the free throw line, and added three steals. Gerald Drumgoole Jr. had nine points and shot 3 for 11, including 1 for 7 from beyond the arc. Kino Lilly Jr. finished with 22 points and four assists for the Bears (1-5). Brown also got 14 points, seven rebounds and two steals from Nana Owusu-Anane. Felix Kloman also put up six points and seven rebounds. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
